text: Metadioctria is a genus of robber flies in the family Asilidae. There are at least three described species in Metadioctria. ==Species== * Metadioctria parvula (Coquillett, 1893) * Metadioctria resplendens (Loew, 1872) * Metadioctria rubida (Coquillett, 1893) ==References== ==Further reading== * * * * * * ==External links== * * Category:Asilidae genera
title: Metadioctria
